nodes.text: Virtuous Velocity was a fathier male that mated with Imperial, who gave birth to the fathier named Shifting Sands in 29 ABY as a result.

By around 34 ABY, Shifting Sands had become a racing fathier on the planet Cantonica. Virtuous Velocity was listed as the fathier's sire on race programs, including one collected by the Resistance mechanic Rose Tico and added to her diary.
Virtuous Velocity was first mentioned in the 2018 replica journal The Last Jedi: Rose Tico: Resistance Fighter, which was written by Jason Fry.
